Package view

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AddPhotoToAlbumController
    Addition of a Photo to the selected Album is handled by this controller
    AddTagController
    Addition of a Tag to the currently selected Photo is handled by this controller, allows to add a new tag by choosing name from preexisting tag names and adding a value to it OR allows user to create a new tag name and add value to it
    AdminController
    Loads the Administrator Dashboard where admin can add, delete and see a list of users.
    AlbumsController
    Loads the Screen with user's list of albums, showing their name, date range and number of photos Handles action to create/delete/rename/display an album or search through all of user's albums
    CopyOrMoveController
    Loads the user to the screen where they can choose to copy or move the selected photo to an album of choice Handles copying and moving a photo from one album to another
    CreateAlbumController
    Loads the user to the screen where they can create a new album Handles user input for a new album name and adds it to user's list of albums if input is valid
    LoginController
    Handles the Login Screen that allows logic for the admin, stock user or a regular user and loads to their individual screens Serializes each user's data and saves it in binary form
    PhotosSlideshowController
    Handles the screen with Photos Slideshow, displays the currently selected photo with its tags and caption.
    RecaptionController
    Handles the screen which allows the user to recaption the selected photo in an album
    RenameAlbumController
    Handles Renaming the selected album
    SearchPhotosController
    Loads the user to the Search for Photos screen that allows the user to search for photos based on tags and dates.
    SearchResultController
    Search Result is displayed using this controller by displaying Photo thumbnails
    SelectedAlbumViewController
    Handles the Selected Album View screen where thumbnails of all photos in the Album are displayed with their caption Manages the actions that can be performed on a selected photo in the album
    ThumbnailCell
    ThumbnailCell extends the ListCell class for a Photo Helps put a Photo and its caption in a cell in the listview
